":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"柒頭黑警以為冇cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af5e91122abef7a5cae4ea449464e82b84eb098","tid":1976285,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558020d9e3b7df676c0558285eaed42550de9160","tid":1976285,"uid":273716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"柒頭黑警以為冇cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"基隆黃嘛<br />\nCCTV容乜易拎<br />\n黑警搞人以為冇後果咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3566a5fabad7ab1860d71d25398fbb1e32c894c4","tid":1976285,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"各位唔好再講鬥黃喇<br />\n對家今次奶西奶著屎<br />\n唔好放過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febc95c509dd192fe31191abd0a36ae977d8e6ce","tid":1976285,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1851437f81203c636564ae04cddd3a35229eedf","tid":1976285,"uid":29107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"但最後會唔會基隆比人告點解無盡責幫入店狗量體溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"正確。<br />\n<br />\n其實之前網上流傳上菜前除口罩俾便衣出吿票嗰陣已經有人講過，《規定及指示（業務及處所）》既指示係適用於餐廳負責人，同理相關刑責都係適用於餐廳負責人。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你上菜前冇戴口罩，罰既係餐廳負責人。同理，如果有人進入餐廳前冇量度體溫，罰既都係餐廳負責人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔知港共有心定無意（可能班離地法律專員真係想像唔到咁多情景），但結論就係咁荒謬。不過香港人習慣食懶人包，冇人認真攞過法律條文去睇，真係有人講嗰陣都搞唔大單野。<br />\n<br />\n詳見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202415e/cs22020241531.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202415e%2Fcs22020241531.pdf&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU96HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=c8a0c16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202415e/cs22020241531.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"42dc5af483515b89f17590cf60ff103288db7ddc","tid":1976285,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"另外誹謗好大部份係民事案件，刑事誹謗係絕無僅有，所以呢單野如果黑警識玩，分分鐘係基隆需要負刑責，黑警最多當賠錢（反正啲錢係納稅人既）"}]}